      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; documented parameter mapping between validation and COU conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Parameter mapping between FDA benchmark conditions and CPB COU documented in assessment report Section 4.3. Dimensional analysis confirms dynamic similarity within acceptable bounds. Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2."
